      "description": "入参`x`、`scale`、`offset`的数据类型不支持BFLOAT16，数据格式不支持NZ。",
      "constraint_detail": "(x.dtype != \"BFLOAT16\" and x.format != \"NZ\") and (scale.dtype != \"BFLOAT16\" and scale.format != \"NZ\") and (offset.dtype != \"BFLOAT16\" and offset.format != \"NZ\")"
    },
    {
      "platform": "<term>Atlas 推理系列产品</term>",
